text: Natasha Liu Bordizzo (; born 25 August 1994) is an Australian actress and model. She is known for her roles as Snow Vase in Netflix's Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon: Sword of Destiny and Helena in Netflix's The Society. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Australian movie actors Category:Australian television actors Category:Australian voice actors Category:Australian models Category:Actors from Sydney
